{"tid":325246,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[嘉許]支那留學生加入美軍 稱「眾叛親離」也值得","createTime":"2017-07-17T05:33:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T05:47:34.000Z","uid":41351,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc558b14af6759a69d736a607d416c6ed6615e5a","tid":325246,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:33:58.000Z","msg":"中國留美學生選擇投筆從戎，用專業報效美國，除了付出體力和知識外，可能還要承受輿論壓力。美國官方單方面解除上千名外籍兵團合約的消息被中國媒體轉載後，中國網民一片罵聲，甚至有人以「叛國者」來稱呼這些外籍募兵。華生劉Allen和于Frank遭遇同樣問題，他們不僅要面對家人質疑、友人反目，甚至相交多年的女友也離他而去。<br />\n劉Allen(前右)從軍的處境並沒有得到家人的認可。(劉Allen提供)<br />\n劉Allen(前右)從軍的處境並沒有得到家人的認可。(劉Allen提供)<br />\n劉Allen六年前從山東來美，在長島霍夫斯特拉大學(Hofstra University)獲會計碩士學位，2016年4月和陸軍簽約，將成為一名全職軍人(Active Duty)。他於1983年出生，今年33歲，至今MAVNI項目的反情報審查杳無音訊，而今年12月他將超齡不能服役。<br />\n雖然承受巨大壓力，但家人也不支持他的決定。父母十分擔心他的前途，經常詢問他何時回國。為了不讓父親擔心，至今未敢告訴從軍受阻事。他多年沒見遠在中國的外婆，外婆身體每況愈下，他很想回國再見外婆。<br />\n<br />\n最讓他寒心的是，前幾日看到外籍募兵或被取消的新聞在陸媒轉載後，網民留下近4000個負面留言，將他們認定為「叛國者」。<br />\n<br />\n另一名華生于Frank表示，從軍是他從小的願望，他喜歡美國的動畫片、自由和文化，因為考慮美國人對軍人的尊重，他報考預備役士兵，並選擇比步兵傷亡率還高的運輸油罐車職位，「我也有父母，但還是簽了約」。<br />\n<br />\n他說在報考陸軍後，一些友人和同學直接將他的微信拉黑，其中一人和他已相識十餘年。他的女友近日也提出分手，「我們都看不到未來，我也不知道能否給她幸福」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6813/2585041\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6813%2F2585041&d=lPKRRz6ssMTRD7aqGbf%2B%2FU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=c5e01687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6813/2585041</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/07/15/4/3758489.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=400&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F4%2F3758489.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D400%26exp%3D3600&h=ae6d40d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/07/15/4/3758490.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=400&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F4%2F3758490.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D400%26exp%3D3600&h=078ff0c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那人玻璃心碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86333bd0b00d00e6badf3eaacd6437511c39cd30","tid":325246,"uid":36029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:40:48.000Z","msg":"吶...吶...我們曾經說好的中國夢呢...都忘了嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36138b33df4a02c04578cd69ef4be385e85d172f","tid":325246,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:41:04.000Z","msg":"脫北者（中國版）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b377aa4bd3438948b8d18bd4cf9d7ca137c1d5b1","tid":325246,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:42:47.000Z","msg":"美軍咩位最好做 後勤個d?"},{"pid":"ab943ce9d2eac096e589658c39b561a5bc1626e3","tid":325246,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:44:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美軍咩位最好做 後勤個d?</blockquote><br />\n唔通情報咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc22f2060b4a9ecd114cd6d850c7967c56f14025","tid":325246,"uid":13281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:46:42.000Z","msg":"希望唔係土共間諜"},{"pid":"732315bf37954eb6cdf933c859a874e012ba2c08","tid":325246,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:47:34.000Z","msg":"其實屌人走狗漢奸嗰d 自己都唔知幾想去<br />\n不過meet 唔到人地個requirement 咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}